data.description: Ready to move into this lovely all brick home situated on approx. 1/3 acre.   Beautiful staircase as you enter the front door.  Spacious living room, with dining room off of the kitchen.  Master bedroom and full bath on the main floor with 2 bedrooms and half bath upstairs.  Large fenced in back yard with patio and beautiful flowers and landscaping to enjoy in the spring and summer.  Extra parking in the back plus a one car garage.  Partial basement.  There is also a hook up in the main bath for a stackable washer and dryer.  Gas f/a furnace & A/C.  The fireplace in the living room has been closed.
